nodes.text: Convoy 8766, also referred to as Convoy Trill, was a convoy of the Galactic Empire's Navy that consisted of four bulk freighters, six medium freighters, and a Victory-class Star Destroyer for security. The convoy arrived at a depot over the course of three days, with the Star Destroyer arriving on the second day. It was rumored that the convoy was headed for a secret Imperial installation. Rebel Alliance agents sought to gain supplies from the convoy.
